       script -- its `, 1` fallback makes the calc a no-op here), so scoping this
       override to just .support-card-expertise and dropping it inside the existing
       <1200px block (this file's own mobile/tablet breakpoint, matching the
       instruction to reuse the file's established convention) changes nothing for
       Capital/Infrastructure/Piloting or for the >=1200px desktop rule above. */
    .support-card-expertise .card-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.6875rem; /* 11px, half of 1.375rem/22px */
    }

    .support-card {
      justify-self: center;
    }

